<p>ì•ì— <a href="https://sweetfood-dev.github.io/algorithm/dp/11726-2-n/">íƒ€ì¼ë§ ë¬¸ì œ</a>ì—ì„œ 2 * 2 íƒ€ì¼ì´ ì¶”ê°€ë˜ì—ˆì„ ë¿ ê°œë…ì€ ê°™ë‹¤
(n - 1)  + (n - 2) * 2 &gt; 2 * 2 íƒ€ì¼ì€ ê²°êµ­ ( n - 2 ) íƒ€ì¼ê³¼ ê°™ë‹¤</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>func solve(n : Int) -&gt; Int {
    if n == 0 { return 0}
    if n == 1 { return 1}
    if n == 2 { return 3}
    var arr = [Int](repeating: 0, count : n + 1)

    arr[1] = 1
    arr[2] = 3
    for i in 3 ... n {
        arr[i] = arr[i - 1] + (arr[i - 2] * 2)
        arr[i] %= 10007
    }
    return arr[n]
}
</code></pre></div></div>
